  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      234.04,
      523.4,
      261.12
    ],
    "text": "Passing Out Ceremony of 280 Apprentice Police Officers Successfully Completing Basic Training",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      275.68,
      504.71,
      330.36
    ],
    "text": "The passing out ceremony of 225 Apprentice Police Constables and 55 Apprentice Police Constable Drivers, who successfully completed their basic training at the Kalutara Police College, was held on 03.04.2026 at the Aluvihara Sports Grounds of the Kalutara Police College.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      344.92,
      520.63,
      399.6
    ],
    "text": "The event was held under the patronage of the Minister of Public Security and Parliamentary Affairs, Mr. Ananda Wijepala, with the participation of the Secretary to the Ministry, retired Senior DIG Mr. Ravi Seneviratne, and the Inspector General of Police, Attorney-at-Law Mr. Priyantha Weerasuriya.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      414.06,
      400.99,
      427.34
    ],
    "text": "The awards for outstanding performance were presented as follows:",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      441.9,
      508.42,
      510.38
    ],
    "text": "\u2022 Best Apprentice Police Constable: 107968 A.M.O.V. Officer Seneviratne \u2022 Best Target Shooter: Police Constable 108087 W.I.S. Bandara \u2022 Best Disciplined Police Constable: 107985 R.M.D.S. Senaratne \u2022 Best Police Constable Driver: 108106 H.M.G.M. Herath \u2022 Best Police Constable Driver (Special Recognition): 108104 R.M.S.T.D. Lanka",
    "fonts": [
      "ArialMT",
      "SymbolMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      9.960000038146973,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      524.82,
      525.82,
      579.53
    ],
    "text": "Officers who demonstrated exceptional performance during the training period were awarded prizes and certificates by the Hon. Minister and the Inspector General of Police. The newly appointed officers were also commended and encouraged to uphold professional excellence, integrity, and dedication in serving the public as disciplined members of the Sri Lanka Police.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      594.09,
      517.31,
      634.97
    ],
    "text": "The passing out ceremony was enriched with a vibrant display of discipline, music, and cultural performances presented by the Police Special Task Force, the Police Western Band, the Police Canine Unit, and talented teams from the Police Academy.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      649.53,
      524.88,
      718.01
    ],
    "text": "The event was attended by Senior DIG Administration Sanjeewa Dharmaratne, Senior DIG Western Province Sajeewa Medawatte, Senior DIG Training and Advanced Training Director Attorney Sampath Kumara Liyanage, DIG Recruitment and Training Director Jagath Seram, senior police officers, other government officials, parents of the trainee officers, and a large gathering of invitees.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      732.47,
      328.99,
